==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Interponent
<hw>In`ter*po"nent</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who, or
that which, interposes; an interloper, an opponent.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark> <rj><au>Heywood.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Interposal</ent>⟦br⟧
